# Muaban Phone Extraction Implementation

The objective is to enable phone number extraction for `muaban.net` listings by implementing a browser-based authentication mechanism (`setup-muaban`) similar to `nhatot`. This session will then be used by the spider to reveal phone numbers that are currently obscured/encrypted.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The phone reveal mechanism on `muaban.net` requires a logged-in session. The user will need to run `python -m cli.main setup-muaban` and perform a manual Google login once to initialize the persistent browser profile.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Auth Client

#### [NEW] [muaban_auth.py](file:///d:/Programming/real-estork/auth/muaban_auth.py)
- Create `MuabanAuthClient` modeled after `NhatotAuthClient` and `BatdongsanAuthClient`.
- Uses Playwright with a persistent browser profile (`.muaban_browser_profile/`).
- Captures cookies and stores them in `.muaban_cookies.json`.

### 2. CLI Integration

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///d:/Programming/real-estork/cli/main.py)
- Add the `setup-muaban` command to allow the user to perform the one-time interactive login.

### 3. Spider Enhancement

#### [MODIFY] [muaban.py](file:///d:/Programming/real-estork/spiders/muaban.py)
- Implement `enrich_listing(listing)` or integrate phone fetch into the main loop.
- Use `MuabanAuthClient` to retrieve the session.
- Call the internal Muaban phone reveal API.
- Update `phone_enc` to actual `phone` digit string.

### 4. Orchestrator Integration

#### [MODIFY] [agent.py](file:///d:/Programming/real-estork/orchestrator/agent.py)
- Initialize `MuabanAuthClient` in `__init__`.
- Update `_check_muaban_token` to perform auto-refresh if possible, or notify user to re-run setup.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `python -m cli.main setup-muaban` (Manual verification of browser launch).
- Scratch script to test `MuabanSpider.enrich_listing` with a real `source_id`.

### Manual Verification
- Verify that Muaban listings in Telegram now contain clear phone numbers instead of empty/masked ones.
- Check `.muaban_cookies.json` after setup.
